<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM9.5">
<l>poruntārkai vēlnutipōṟ paraṟpāya mellaṭikaḷ kuruti cōra</l>
<l>virumpāta kāṉvirumpi veyiluṟaippa vempacinōy kūra viṉṟu</l>
<l>perumpāvi yēṉmakaṉē pōkiṉṟāy kēkayarkōṉ makaḷāyp peṟṟa</l>
<l>varumpāvi coṟkēṭṭa varuviṉaiyē ṉeṉceykē ṉantō yāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Son of me, who am a great sinner! You are going today,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [Your] soft feet exude blood</l>
<l rend="indent">as the stones pierce like the tips of spears in the hands of the enemies</l>
<l>desiring the undesirable jungle,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the heat and the glare of the sun burn,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the cruel pain of hunger is excessive!</l>
<l>What shall I do,</l>
<l rend="indent">[I] who have uncommon karma,</l>
<l rend="indent">who listened to the words of the hardened sinner</l>
<l rend="indent">whom the king of Kēkayas begot as a daughter? Alas!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
